# Authentication Logic Flaw Testing – DVWA

## Objective
Test authentication flow for logic vulnerabilities.

## Tools
Burp Suite
Kali Linux
DVWA

## Methodology
1. Captured login request with Burp Proxy
2. Sent request to Repeater
3. Manipulated parameters
4. Tested missing parameters
5. Tested duplicate parametersDrag and drop operation from guest to host failed.

## Findings
Application accepted malformed authentication requests.

## Impact
Attackers may bypass authentication checks.

## Mitigation
- Strict server-side validation
- Reject missing parameters
- Validate authentication flow properly
